<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>User Activation</title>
        <style>
            body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f9f9f9; color: #333; }
            .container { max-width: 500px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);}
            .otp { font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold; color: #2d8cf0; letter-spacing: 6px; }
            .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #888; }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
            <p>Thank you for registering with us!</p>
            <p>Your One-Time Password (OTP) for account activation is:</p>
            <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
            <p>Please enter this OTP to complete your registration. This code is valid for a limited time.</p>
            <div class="footer">
                If you did not request this, please ignore this email.<br>
                &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SPRINT FLOW All rights reserved.<br>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>